<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢١٨٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3919">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مَسْلَمَةَ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2177">زَيْدِ بْنِ ثَابِتٍ </a><span class="special">﵃</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: أَرْخَصَ لِصَاحِبِ الْعَرِيَّةِ أَنْ يَبِيعَهَا بِخَرْصِهَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>